text: Anthony Akumu Agai (born 20 October 1992) is a Kenyan professional footballer who plays for Kaizer Chiefs, as a midfielder, as well as the Kenyan national team. ==Career== Born in Rachuonyo, Akumu has played club football for Gor Mahia, Al Khartoum and ZESCO United. In January 2020 he moved to Kaizer Chiefs.
